  lines:
  - speaker: You
    line: "You have a pretty high bounty on your head. Considering what you did to
      those people I\u2019d say it's warranted."
    SpriteRange: 5
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: "I\u2019d say they had it coming. "
    SpriteRange: 3
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: After all, they were rather rude liars.
    SpriteRange: 3
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: "Now I\u2019m curious to know what your intentions are."
    SpriteRange: 4
